O '''giv''' (vai ''giu'', ''gesu'', ''div'') si ek [[char]] so si o mai importanto xaben manushengo. 

==Anav==
O lav si [[Indo-ariaynikane ćhiba|indo-ariyanikano]] ([[sanskrit]]: गोधूमा - godhuma; [[hindi ćhib|hindikanes]]: गेहूं - gehun).

==Puranipen==
Anglunes, le manusha baryarden o giv andi [[Sudvestutni Asiya]], 10,000 [[bersh]]a anglal. 5.000 bersha anglal, lesko baryaripen avilo ande [[Ethiopia]], [[Indiya]], [[Irland]] thai [[Spaniya]]. Palal 1,000 bersha avilo vi andi [[China]].

